1. If we use more than one transform ona single element, they must be contained within the same line and if you do add hover effect,
the hover will need to contain both trasnform property values.

2. Normal state

  .story__img {
    height: 100%;
    transform: translateX(-4rem) scale(1.4);
    backface-visibility: hidden;
    transition: all .5s; }
    
    
3. Hover state

 .story:hover .story__img {
    transform: translateX(-4rem) scale(1); }
